hopobject.body: We went to university together labrada muscle mass gainer side effects The airline acknowledged that what transpired between the mom and the flight attendant should have been "more consistent" with what's in the flight attendant manual. The manual reads, "If a customer's activity causes discomfort to another customer, F/As should use their best judgment to decide whether the activity is inappropriate. A F/A may be called upon to relocate an offended customer to another seat or discretely inform a customer of airline policy. In instances involving customer discomfort, F/As should use the following guidelines to determine the best course of action."
